
Dependencies:
  Scons
  Python (for SCons)
  SDL-devel
  SDL_gfx

ALL PLATFORMS:

1. Install SCons
2. Install SDL-devel (Windows users, see instructions below)
3. Bring up a command line, and enter the command 'scons'

WINDOWS BUILD:

Download SDL-devel-1.2.13-VC8.zip from http://www.libsdl.org/release/SDL-devel-1.2.13-VC8.zip

Unzip the contents into the project's folder, and rename this folder to just SDL.
